---
layout: layout.njk
title: Home
permalink: /
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Learn of Me</h1>
  <p class="verse">"Take my yoke upon you, and learn of me; for I am meek and lowly in heart: and ye shall find rest unto your souls."
    <span class="cite">— Matthew 11:29</span>
  </p>
</section>

<main>
  <p>Welcome. This is a home for music, teaching, and Bible study — anything that points people to Christ and helps advance His Kingdom. Whether you're here to listen, learn, or study with us, may you find rest here.</p>

  <div class="doors">
    <div class="door">
      <h3>Episodes</h3>
      <p>Questions the Bible answers. Each study takes a passage and lays multiple teachers side by side — listen and learn from them all.</p>
      <a href="/episodes/">Explore episodes &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="door">
      <h3>Teachers</h3>
      <p>Meet the voices. Trusted Bible expositors and evangelists whose teachings we study, compare, and learn from side by side.</p>
      <a href="/teachers/">Meet the voices &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="door">
      <h3>We Sing Jesus</h3>
      <p>Original songs written and sung to lift up the name of Jesus. Listen through the built-in player.</p>
      <a href="/we-sing-jesus/">Listen &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% if episodes.published.length > 0 %}
  <h2>Latest Episodes</h2>
  {% for ep in episodes.published | reverse %}
  {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
  <div class="episode-card">
    <div class="episode-card-top">
      {% if ep.category %}
      <span class="category-badge small">{{ ep.category }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <h3><a href="/episodes/{{ ep.slug }}/">{{ ep.question }}</a></h3>
    <div class="meta">
      <span class="passage">{{ ep.scripture }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="teachers-list">
      {% for teacher in ep.teachers | split(",") %}
      <span class="teacher-tag">{{ teacher }}</span>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% if ep.audio_url %}
    <div class="episode-audio-badge">
      <span>&#9654; Deep dive available</span>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
  <div class="empty-state">
    <p>Episodes are on the way. Check back soon.</p>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</main>
